description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: Doing Fireball Shots At Satancon with Beer City Bruiser!!

Dun, Dun.... Runnin' with the Devil!! With all apologies to Van Halen, this episode of Supernatural News/ Parashare is HOT! Now, I am gonna reach down.... between my legs.... and ... grab the news stories!! You filthy kids!! We got a wild week in the News and Cruiser and Bruiser are hard at work again!  

This week,  Satancon is back on like Donkey Kong downing Sean Don and bon bons! (we'll let you use that one with your crew), we'll tell you the reason it was too hot to hold it last year,  We will play you the terrifying sound of... SPACE! (if by terrifying you mean not being able to get off the toilet...), and the state of NJ is bulldozing a haunted school (spoiler: that trick never ends well!) PLUS: some of the creepiest ghost stories ever heard!
